	   <tr><td colspan=2>Damage bonus is based on skill (for melee class's only!)<br><br>Damage bonus is basicly your minimum damage when you hit.<br><br>*Non-melee classes don't get a damage bonus<br><br>*All lvl 60 melee classes have a Damage bonus of 11 on a 1h weapon<br><br>*Damage bonus on 2h Weapons is based upon the delay.<br><br>So when you see a guy running around auc that his 10/40 2hs is really good because it has a damage bonus of 30 making it a 40/40 he is lying.&nbsp;&nbsp;For him he would still be using a 10/40 but his min. hit would be 30.<br><br>I have just seen this confused WAY too much.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
